  org.qi4j.spi.structure.DescriptorVisitor<ThrowableType>

public class DescriptorVisitor<ThrowableType extends Throwable>
extends Object

Extend and override this class in order to introspect a Qi4j model. Call ApplicationSPI.visitDescriptor(DescriptorVisitor) to use.
